{"tid":1631824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔講咁多，請入黎重陽節俾個開花時間","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:58.000Z","uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b15af6d382ed2a054f635b5847ab3436da839f6f","tid":1631824,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"1300？<br />\n1500？<br />\n2000？<br />\n<br />\n請留低你既理想時間"},{"pid":"9b0a529f78ac088849db4f6dc3e233dc399ba170","tid":1631824,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52afc6f465d221759dd7a5d477c073f98f4037d6","tid":1631824,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81da6a0077c5dfbd6161d4870284425e72f2b62a","tid":1631824,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0994f13df07622e877e9dd192f5c681e139d04","tid":1631824,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47cff5a200b3b4eaaac7bfc1dd64ca2c476fe04","tid":1631824,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8c7b46d153604ab536749b7f685bd50066a102eb","tid":1631824,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"各區谷自行決定"},{"pid":"95b49bbe08bb1ed8a97a096e8782066abc7c963f","tid":1631824,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3f14ccda9a7ef68d85fc0f459d382952c1434e","tid":1631824,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"出面講左啦同一時間 推其他有用post仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef61173ccf7d8d6626537f91fc80658af8de334c","tid":1631824,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02a673b5c96e71447aa4d655afec94ff34ed8853","tid":1631824,"uid":227441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"ooiwnknfk"},{"pid":"6aca1f4ade5277e0106cee28e172894bca3eb626","tid":1631824,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"dcdc9329eb1ab925cf22b6c7b0fa60027d067105","tid":1631824,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c7b46d153604ab536749b7f685bd50066a102eb","tid":1631824,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"各區谷自行決定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"就係自己區谷想跟返大隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想有手足出去早場返唔到黎好似今日咁"},{"pid":"6f918d5ffd1aa5c5aa96a7858512a4349822f085","tid":1631824,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef61173ccf7d8d6626537f91fc80658af8de334c","tid":1631824,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"早會唔會更加好？<br />\n出其不意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7276ea6b90b526a47a7f8467121f3e94feda3e78","tid":1631824,"uid":140917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"三點"},{"pid":"960bff5400760bb04994b75a2dabb733be1f0ae3","tid":1631824,"uid":294783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"乜冇人睇到咩?鬼鬼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂!係咪我睇錯呀?幫下眼望望唔該!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/000905_017a6e3e60c682d464bbf9a17962c350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F000905_017a6e3e60c682d464bbf9a17962c350.jpg&h=6b004ccc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a6e63eeb2ebf537c8a36ce1a1e12736f6915811","tid":1631824,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}